Hello, my name is Ethan Wang-So, and I am a student, programmer, and amateur web designer. I am currently based in New York.

Education

I am involved with the Association for Computing Machinery and Filipinos In Newark Engaging In Socio-Cultural Traditions. I have done research on campus in the virtual reality facility under Dr. Margarita Vinnikov. I am also a Teacher's Assistant in the computer science department.



I graduated high school at St. Peter's Preparatory School in Jersey City, New Jersey.

Skills & Experience
